dc_title_s: Oil Seed Processing Plants: United States, Fall 2014
dc_description_s: This point dataset shows the locations of oil seed processing plants in the United States. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for renewable and electric energy in the U.S. This layer is from the 2014 Fall Quarter update (Update 1017).This shapefile can be used to locate and analyze existing Oilseed Processing Plants used in the developemtn of Biodiesel.
